{"tid":2436814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4月15日黨安法安全教育日一齊請假！","createTime":"2021-03-07T12:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T14:43:32.000Z","uid":207900,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0b5e1bc6054186d2ac166d935a0b6b8df1e533db","tid":2436814,"uid":207900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"黨安法之後，4.15罷教/罷課一定會比人批鬥。香港人係咪一定要睇住下一代受到荼毒？<br />\n<br />\n如果你係老師，你當日應該會唔舒服，記得請假睇醫生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你係學生，你當日又咁啱唔舒服，記得請假睇醫生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你係家長，如果仔女唔舒服，記得幫佢地請假睇醫生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過如果你想了解或推廣全民國家安全教育日，咁就記住準時返工返學啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578990-20210305.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578990-20210305.htm&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=ad932929\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578990-20210305.htm&h=f6c38a63\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578990-20210305.htm</a>"},{"pid":"061ae2a72a160716eef7a1b62e645230818f055f","tid":2436814,"uid":207900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:07:40.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"4e806f977fbe05c616230d92aab74644d8e9c2f0","tid":2436814,"uid":207900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:08:08.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"abf4cc3060b75c40bd3b657c264eabfd277affba","tid":2436814,"uid":207900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"可唔可以幫手推一推？"},{"pid":"4b798ca5d15010189a9d0de24444059d00c9aaf7","tid":2436814,"uid":207900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime